<!--more-->I found them buzzing around one of the bushes next to the front door. Asia found them, too, and was pacing below, looking for a chance to pounce on one.

This is a cat that tries to pounce on anything bigger than an ant, but with the coordination of spasmodic pile of furry Jell-o.

